title: GoogleEuicc don't support China Unicom because no CA certificates
content:
Chinese carrier China Unicom and China Mobile use their own CAs for esim sm-dp+ server
GoogleEuicc(com.google.android.euicc) don't have their CA certificates, so connection will fail at first.

sm-dp+ domain: esim.wo.com.cn

I SHOULD feed back to the developement team, however I just can't find any way to do so.
or my feedback just never gain an reply...

so i write here.
